rs" class="answers text-muted">3 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/yuxi624" data-hovercard='p$t$yuxi624'>禹汐</a><span class="icon icon-badge-identity icon-badge" data-tooltip="s$b$已认证的个人"></span><div class="bio">中国医科大学附属第一医院皮肤科 <span class="bull">&bull;</span> 医师</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/sanjiayifly" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$sanjiayifly'><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-dec7eb7423f89bb819ed123f26c09068_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="Gigi"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/guomin/sanjiayifly/answers" class="answers text-muted">3 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/sanjiayifly" data-hovercard='p$t$sanjiayifly'>Gigi</a><div class="bio">L’OREAL CHINA <span class="bull">&bull;</span> 科学家</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/hu-xiao-bo-1025" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$hu-xiao-bo-1025'><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/260a51caa7e978390ffa2d7c3a6a98e7_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="胡晓波"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/guomin/hu-xiao-bo-1025/answers" class="answers text-muted">4 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/hu-xiao-bo-1025" data-hovercard='p$t$hu-xiao-bo-1025'>胡晓波</a><div class="bio">各种理性谈论（吐槽）护肤品。公众号：配方师Rex。</div></div></div></li></ul></div></div><div class="module participants"><div class="module-header"><h3>热门回答者</h3></div><div class="module-body"><ul class="items-fulid"><li class="item"><a href="/people/liu-ruo-lin-98" class="item-link" data-hovercard='p$t$liu-ruo-lin-98'><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/fafd738d208920c8a7f5e4a9c2cd1fc0_l.jpg" alt="柳若琳" class="avatar d50"></a></li><li class="item"><a href="/people/sijiazhao" class="item-link" data-hovercard='p$t$sijiazhao'><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/35603b3f94319b308d28b600fa5e25c3_l.jpg" alt="赵思家" class="avatar d50"></a></li><li class="item"><a href="/people/karanokyoukai" class